                <p>Checking the Delta flight status online helps you stay informed about your flight’s real-time updates. This is especially useful for planning your trip, knowing if your flight is delayed, or if there are any schedule changes, so you can adjust your travel plans accordingly.</p>
                <h3>Can I track my Delta flight status from anywhere?</h3>
                <p>Yes, you can track your Delta flight status from anywhere, either through the Delta website or the mobile app, as long as you have internet access.</p>
